@AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Provider endpoint - simulates slow external API
GET {{AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress}}/provider/pricing?delayMs=1000
Accept: application/json

###

### PoC A - BAD: Does NOT propagate cancellation token
GET {{AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress}}/offers/bad
Accept: application/json

###

### PoC A - GOOD: Propagates cancellation token
GET {{AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress}}/offers/good
Accept: application/json

###

### PoC B - BAD: Does NOT check cancellation in loop
GET {{AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress}}/combinations/bad
Accept: application/json

###

### PoC B - GOOD: Checks cancellation token in loop
GET {{AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress}}/combinations/good
Accept: application/json

###

### PoC C: Linked cancellation (request OR timeout)
GET {{AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress}}/offers/timeout?timeoutMs=3000
Accept: application/json

###

### Task.WhenAll: Parallel provider aggregation
GET {{AsyncCallsApi_HostAddress}}/offers/parallel
Accept: application/json

###

